=center|1\n|-\n|align=center|[[Mu\u015f Province|Mu\u015f]]\n|align=center|11\n|align=center|0\n|-\n|align=center|[[Nev\u015fehir Province|Nev\u015fehir]]\n|align=center|18\n|align=center|0\n|-\n|align=center|[[Ni\u011fde Province|Ni\u011fde]]\n|align=center|3\n|align=center|0\n|-\n|align=center|[[Ordu Province|Ordu]]\n|align=center|73\n|align=center|0\n|-\n|align=center|[[Osmaniye Province|Osmaniye]]\n|align=center|31\n|align=center|1\n|-\n|align=center|[[Rize Province|Rize]]\n|align=center|88\n|align=center|3\n|-\n|align=center|[[Sakarya Province|Sakarya]]\n|align=center|207\n|align=center|3\n|-\n|align=center|[[Samsun Province|Samsun]]\n|align=center|112\n|align=center|1\n|-\n|align=center|[[Siirt Province|Siirt]]\n|align=center|32\n|align=center|0\n|-\n|align=center|[[Sinop Province|Sinop]]\n|align=center|31\n|align=center|1\n|-\n|align=center|[[Sivas Province|Sivas]]\n|align=center|67\n|align=center|1\n|-\n|align=center|[[\u015eanl\u0131urfa Province|\u015eanl\u0131urfa]]\n|align=center|11\n|align=center|0\n|-\n|align=center|[[\u015e\u0131rnak Province|\u015e\u0131rnak]]\n|align=center|3\n|align=center|0\n|-\n|align=center|[[Tekirda\u011f Province|Tekirda\u011f]]\n|align=center|101\n|align=center|0\n|-\n|align=center|[[Tokat Province|Tokat]]\n|align=center|80\n|align=center|3\n|-\n|align=center|[[Trabzon Province|Trabzon]]\n|align=center|74\n|align=center|5\n|-\n|align=center|[[Tunceli Province|Tunceli]]\n|align=center|6\n|align=center|0\n|-\n|align=center|[[U\u015fak Province|U\u015fak]]\n|align=center|38\n|align=center|1\n|-\n|align=center|[[Van Province|Van]]\n|align=center|26\n|align=center|0\n|-\n|align=center|[[Yalova Province|Yalova]]\n|align=center|46\n|align=center|0\n|-\n|align=center|[[Yozgat Province|Yozgat]]\n|align=center|13\n|align=center|2\n|-\n|align=center|[[Zonguldak Province|Zonguldak]]\n|align=center|112\n|align=center|5\n|}\n </div>\n{{notelist}}\n\n===Graphs===\n{{Graph:Chart\n|type=line\n|linewidth=1\n|showSymbols=1\n|width=850\n|colors=